gclid%3DCj0KCQjwnNvaBRCmARIsAOfZq-0FMjZA1V3OeDbN5VYNLUD1xYxOoI-itJQzzWHOY_-pD_ODMKNTEIwaAkNMEALw_wcB&d=%2FrI7eD%2F6V29ZkNZAC5nNgMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=1f42a239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bookdepository.com/The-Only-Way-to-Stop-Smoking-Permanently-Allen-Carr/9781405916387?redirected=true&amp;utm_medium=Google&amp;utm_campaign=Base1&amp;utm_source=HK&amp;utm_content=The-Only-Way-to-Stop-Smoking-Permanently&amp;selectCurrency=HKD&amp;w=AFF1AU96D2XDTGA80RX7&amp;pdg=pla-310400086064:kwd-310400086064:cmp-803315232:adg-43197004058:crv-190692855543:pid-9781405916387:dev-c&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwnNvaBRCmARIsAOfZq-0FMjZA1V3OeDbN5VYNLUD1xYxOoI-itJQzzWHOY_-pD_ODMKNTEIwaAkNMEALw_wcB</a> <br />\n<br />\n6月29號食完最後一支, dum撚埋火機, 到今日都無諗過食返<br />\n無食一星期開始個人已經精神左好多, 經過有人食煙仲會覺得好撚臭<br />\n<br />\n祝巴打戒煙成功!"},{"pid":"6dad6a8fadf22cb54b9d5a098d6c6b02ef5a28bb","tid":754167,"uid":33655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"忍住唔買煙"},{"pid":"19a435e478883c660195e22e0fe5eab3d5e4e263","tid":754167,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9c42e28ef1ce0ceb3970762217eef6098fb84c","tid":754167,"uid":14910,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"833fe11f4380fd66bc1fb981fce3e597048db2ed","tid":754167,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"有事要做手術<br />\n就會緊張健康<br />\n<br />\n（手術唔關食煙事）"},{"pid":"235ed906587ddc1b1c03038985e7e13408cd616c","tid":754167,"uid":92690,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"食左十三年，當中戒過幾次，最長一年，而家完全戒左接近四五年。我每次戒都係順其自然去戒，無用任何什麼戒煙貼同口交之類既野幫助，眼見好多朋友用都無咩效，因為其實係幫到你頂一陣癮，但過左效都係頂唔到，聽講呢d代替品入面尼古丁含量仲高過一支煙。<br />\n<br />\n首先第一步要掉晒d火機，煙灰缸同所有同吸煙習慣有關既野先，清潔屋企等唔好有煙味殘留。<br />\n<br />\n第二步要遠離煙友，我次次戒左又食返都係因為同煙友一齊果陣，因睇住佢食一路傾計就自然好想食返，戒煙初期必定要自閉一排。<br />\n<br />\n第三步就係要戒埋酒，因為一飲左酒意志就會鬆懈，好容易又食返，有好多戒煙研究建議戒煙一定要戒埋酒，識好多人平時唔食煙無煙癒，但飲左酒就會食，最少等你完全唔會再有煙癮起先好飲返。<br />\n<br />\n最後要記住，唔好諗住自己戒到一次就戒到第二次呢個想法，只要你一掂返，扯返第一口煙既時候，就註定你會失敗，就好似俾魔鬼戰勝左自己，只會越吸越兇狠，我最後戒煙前果一次，份量已經去到一日二至三包，身體都比同年齡既人退化得多，但到今日身體機能比之前叫做好左d，希望巴打你成功戒到！"},{"pid":"12ef93f1eecba0d1d08879eeb67e4b1c0fbd9ab4","tid":754167,"uid":74686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"每次想買煙個時就買其他同等價值嘅嘢"},{"pid":"3d7ef4d4924c4cb8ae90be2d5aa7416a7cace448","tid":754167,"uid":92690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:29:35.000Z","msg":"補充，只要你頂到頭四日至一星期，煙癮就會減少好多"},{"pid":"026800cc30e276cb9e48b1e6ebd03d5e15c99871","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"感謝咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戒左一日已經開始會少少燥底同埋吊癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef6610ddb2cc9412fb00f4d295de06b390960c0","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"833fe11f4380fd66bc1fb981fce3e597048db2ed","tid":754167,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"有事要做手術<br />\n就會緊張健康<br />\n<br />\n（手術唔關食煙事）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"我就係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a403b54de24d4233a9b1a0df128e7f86a39b1b","tid":754167,"uid":55308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"本身食左4年<br />\n<br />\n轉左工成個環境都無人食, 而且都好唔方便<br />\n身邊D朋友都戒左<br />\n慢慢食得越黎越少<br />\n<br />\n後來仲識左個女仔, 決心戒煙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家5個月無食, 同自己講每一日都係紀錄, 紀錄係要黎破<br />\n有時做野好攰或者做完當日既野都好想食返支煙放鬆下<br />\n忍住就係"},{"pid":"cb320b1df34dc00ccb3a5f8187b3c0c47e1e036e","tid":754167,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"我冇食但睇身邊d人覺得呢d都係睇決心姐<br />\n男朋友老豆食左幾十年煙<br />\n身體突然有事差d GG <br />\n嚇撚到佢即刻介 佢地勸左佢幾多年都冇用<br />\n衰d講唔見棺材唔流眼淚 <br />\n希望ching唔洗去到呢個地步先介到啦"},{"pid":"ae8cdc67186467722ba54dad84716cfba328097c","tid":754167,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n轉返5仔，慢慢食1仔<br />\n宜家對煙冇乜引，幾日先食半支仲要覺得難食"},{"pid":"bbd8b50429bde080ed769a2521a5a7bac5377f55","tid":754167,"uid":92690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ef6610ddb2cc9412fb00f4d295de06b390960c0","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"833fe11f4380fd66bc1fb981fce3e597048db2ed","tid":754167,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"有事要做手術<br />\n就會緊張健康<br />\n<br />\n（手術唔關食煙事）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"我就係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意講身體有咩毛病要戒煙？"},{"pid":"e768a0e1455b4b5d336ba2c633196626e1c8767d","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd8b50429bde080ed769a2521a5a7bac5377f55","tid":754167,"uid":92690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ef6610ddb2cc9412fb00f4d295de06b390960c0","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"833fe11f4380fd66bc1fb981fce3e597048db2ed","tid":754167,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"有事要做手術<br />\n就會緊張健康<br />\n<br />\n（手術唔關食煙事）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"我就係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意講身體有咩毛病要戒煙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"睾丸癌<br />\n雖然好似唔關事但有日諗通左就想戒"},{"pid":"cffe65f9e1834f6ae651e113b3655c9d00e8fb4a","tid":754167,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:24:52.000Z","msg":"第一 環境<br />\n第二 搵野分散你既注意力<br />\n隨時隨地唔食半年一半<br />\n再食返都得 <br />\n<br />\n你有煙引起 係因為你習慣左 <br />\n因為乜乜乜，所以你會咁咁咁 <br />\n而你平時咁咁咁果震 係有支煙係手<br />\n但你而家無 所以就羅羅攣 好想食<br />\n搵野分散，工作煩惱 <br />\n唔好比自己抖<br />\n做左先。 <br />\n唔好試咩貼 咩減輕 無用<br />\n只會有依賴性質"},{"pid":"1420ce1d57770396cc32edea5a60d25b23e87f8a","tid":754167,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e768a0e1455b4b5d336ba2c633196626e1c8767d","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd8b50429bde080ed769a2521a5a7bac5377f55","tid":754167,"uid":92690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ef6610ddb2cc9412fb00f4d295de06b390960c0","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"我就係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意講身體有咩毛病要戒煙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"睾丸癌<br />\n雖然好似唔關事但有日諗通左就想戒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:23:44.000Z","msg":"咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身體健康真係最重要，希望師兄你大步覽過"},{"pid":"51ad3cd7957d6efb09c7f635ead32b283d9700b6","tid":754167,"uid":18566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:27:18.000Z","msg":"戒左8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n堅定d啦巴打"},{"pid":"f73e2415c18f4e9029270b246c134c2f0758fa8a","tid":754167,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:02:14.000Z","msg":"返工第一枝點戒都戒唔到<br />\n我廿尾，alevel開始食<br />\n啱啱出嚟做嘢嗰陣仲係一日半包<br />\n呢兩年一日兩三枝，但就係戒唔到"},{"pid":"ca7c8736f6afb644ee6c7b4a816c26b04fcb2209","tid":754167,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73e2415c18f4e9029270b246c134c2f0758fa8a","tid":754167,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T19:02:14.000Z","msg":"返工第一枝點戒都戒唔到<br />\n我廿尾，alevel開始食<br />\n啱啱出嚟做嘢嗰陣仲係一日半包<br />\n呢兩年一日兩三枝，但就係戒唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"其實食咁少有冇問題<br />\n我都好鐘意收工行出office果下食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ded54d336ae983b5a253b4bc5aa5d02182afe80","tid":754167,"uid":191542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"狂做運動"},{"pid":"3100f4a45e065943a4193da546f4316278c2216c","tid":754167,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"唔食咪唔食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明戒煙有幾難<br />\n<br />\n1.試幾次唔食一排<br />\n例如1星期至1個月試下水溫<br />\n呢個試唔係試「戒煙」<br />\n而係攞個感覺<br />\n試下吊煙癮個個感覺有幾辛苦<br />\n<br />\n2.跟住習慣呢個吊煙癮既感覺<br />\n<br />\n3.做好準備，AKA 慣咗吊煙癮 <br />\n同 <br />\n未來會有好多個鍾頭都會吊煙癮既心理準備<br />\n<br />\n4.完全唔食<br />\n<br />\n5.恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好諗你要開始戒<br />\n而係你由下決心呢一刻已經戒咗<br />\n<br />\n申翻利 90後 07年 中1食煙 17年甩咗<br />\n共10年煙齡<br />\n朋友老豆廿幾三十年煙齡都係咁戒"},{"pid":"c205a113584445a1982d9a8dbc81ba7358c80a6a","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/154755_34a1787bbf15fca1d420958e0bce808c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F154755_34a1787bbf15fca1d420958e0bce808c.png&h=e49a9788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經買左呢本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd069ac64d42d4d6c6f0df0704d8b34d6d93020","tid":754167,"uid":130586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"識到陳凱琳掛<br />\n<br />\n利申 睇新聞見到"},{"pid":"937c5ccb1b37d72ede326e85a4a13b24ab579635","tid":754167,"uid":68,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"今日已經係第七日<br />\n本書已經睇完 對自己黎講係有意想不到嘅功效<br />\n唔敢講自己成功左<br />\n但起碼已經係冇欲望去食煙<br />\n